					<p>Perry is a San Luis Obispo native, graduated from California Polytechnic State University in 2019. She has worked at SLO Groove since, teaching many different genres. Perry trained at many local dance studios, and found us when she was looking to take a dance class. She has certification in Zumba and years of ballet, tap, and jazz experience. Perry teaches many different classes at the studio, but she is our only Zumba intsructor!  </p>
                
